data.description: Versatile Half Duplex in the desirable Glenbrook neighborhood.  The Private Gate opens onto the front Courtyard and covered Porch leading you to the home's entry.  Large Living Room with mirror accented wall with Fireplace.  Step up to the Dining Room which is adjacent to the Kitchen.  The well laid out Kitchen has stainless appliances, stylish hardware, double sink and door to Backyard.  2 Masters, 1 up and 1 down.  The downstairs Master is currently being used as 2nd Living Area.  Both feature ample storage and Full Baths.  Upstairs Master is large enough for seating and also features a fireplace.  The Downstairs Master is adjacent to the Study/3rd Bed and Enclosed Patio/Florida Room.  The Swimming Pool and Covered Patio make for great outdoor living spaces.  The location is simply fantastic.  Walking distance to Classen Curve and Nichols Hills Plaza.  Don't miss your chance to call this wonderful property HOME!
